name: $status
desc: Returns: The status code returned by processing this entry. The status SHALL start with a 3 digit HTTP code (e.g. 404) and may contain the standard HTTP description associated with the status code.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The status code returned by processing this entry. The status SHALL start with a 3 digit HTTP code (e.g. 404) and may contain the standard HTTP description associated with the status code.

name: $location
desc: Returns: The location header created by processing this operation, populated if the operation returns a location.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The location header created by processing this operation, populated if the operation returns a location.

name: $etag
desc: Returns: The Etag for the resource, if the operation for the entry produced a versioned resource (see [Resource Metadata and Versioning](http.html#versioning) and [Managing Resource Contention](http.html#concurrency)).

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The Etag for the resource, if the operation for the entry produced a versioned resource (see [Resource Metadata and Versioning](http.html#versioning) and [Managing Resource Contention](http.html#concurrency)).

name: $lastModified
desc: Returns: The date/time that the resource was modified on the server.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The date/time that the resource was modified on the server.

name: $outcome
desc: Returns: An OperationOutcome containing hints and warnings produced as part of processing this entry in a batch or transaction.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: An OperationOutcome containing hints and warnings produced as part of processing this entry in a batch or transaction.
